## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture the full spectrum of strategies employed by independent filmmakers globally. The data is also limited to English-language sources and may not reflect practices in non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the financial landscape for filmmakers can vary significantly based on geographic location, making some strategies more viable in certain areas than others.